  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Fire</b> or <b>flame</b> may refer to:\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Aerion_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerion Targaryen\">Aerion Targaryen</a>, a prince known as Aerion Brightflame and Aerion Brightfire</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Azor_Ahai\" title=\"Azor Ahai\">Azor Ahai</a>, a legendary hero known as the Son of Fire and the warrior of fire</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Moqorro\" title=\"Moqorro\">Moqorro</a>, a red priest known as Black Flame</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Ball\" title=\"Quentyn Ball\">Quentyn Ball</a>, a knight known as Fireball</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Dayne\" title=\"Samwell Dayne\">Samwell Dayne</a>, a Dornish king known as the Starfire</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Others\">Others</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Others\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Fire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle of Fire\">Battle of Fire</a>, term coined by fans for the upcoming battle in Meereen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Blood_and_Fire\" title=\"Blood and Fire\">Blood and Fire</a>, a book about dragons</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dragonglass\" title=\"Dragonglass\">Dragonglass</a>, also known as \"frozen fire\"</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dragonflame\" title=\"Dragonflame\">Dragonflame</a>, the fire produced by dragons</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Field_of_Fire\" title=\"Field of Fire\">Field of Fire</a>, a battle during Aegon's Conquest</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Category:Fire_in_heraldry\" title=\"Category:Fire in heraldry\">Fire</a> as a heraldic charge</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Firemage\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Firemage\">Firemage</a>, magic user with some ability to manipulate fire</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Firemilk\" title=\"Firemilk\">Firemilk</a>, a medical ointment</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fireplum\" title=\"Fireplum\">Fireplum</a>, a type of plum grown in the Reach</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Firepod\" title=\"Firepod\">Firepod</a> a type of plants</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Firewyrm\" title=\"Firewyrm\">Firewyrm</a> a creature that breathe fire</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood,_Being_a_History_of_the_Targaryen_Kings_of_Westeros\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood, Being a History of the Targaryen Kings of Westeros\">Fire &amp; Blood, Being a History of the Targaryen Kings of Westeros</a></i>, a book about House Targaryen</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_Upon_the_Grass\" title=\"Fire Upon the Grass\">Fire Upon the Grass</a></i>, a books about the Dothraki</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Fires_of_the_Freehold\" title=\"The Fires of the Freehold\">The Fires of the Freehold</a></i>, a book about the history of the Valyrian Freehold</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire_(Yandel)\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire (Yandel)\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, a book by Maester Yandel</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Flame\" title=\"Flame\">Flame</a>, a horse owned by Lady Rohanne Webber</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Category:Flame_in_heraldry\" title=\"Category:Flame in heraldry\">Flame</a>, a heraldic tincture</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Flame_of_Truth\" title=\"Flame of Truth\">Flame of Truth</a>, a title held by Benerro</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Frostfires\" title=\"Frostfires\">Frostfires</a>, a species of autumn wildflower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Myrish_fire\" title=\"Myrish fire\">Myrish fire</a>, a medical ointment</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pinchfire\" title=\"Pinchfire\">Pinchfire</a>, a type of plant</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a>, a god also known as the \"Heart of Fire\" and the \"God of Flame and Shadow\"</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_song_of_ice_and_fire\" title=\"The song of ice and fire\">The song of ice and fire</a>, a subject of a prophecy</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">Wildfire</a>, a flammable liquid</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>George R. R. Martin's and derived works:\n</p>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Calendar\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar\">A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Campaign_Guide\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide\">A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying\">A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire:_Tactics\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire: Tactics\">A Song of Ice and Fire: Tactics</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_and_Blood_(TV)\" title=\"Fire and Blood (TV)\">\"Fire and Blood\" (TV)</a></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Art_of_George_R._R._Martin%27s_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Art of George R. R. Martin&#39;s A Song of Ice and Fire\">The Art of George R. R. Martin's A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404151110\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 11/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 16/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:37845-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404151110 and revision id 331974\n -->\n",
